Background

		Mr. Marco Antonio Slim Domit, also known as Tony, serves as the President of The Carlos Slim Health Institute. Mr. Slim Domit serves as General Manager and General Director of Grupo Financiero Inbursa SAB de CV. Mr. Slim Domit served as the President of Impulsora del Desarrollo y el Empleo en América Latina, S.A.B. de C.V. Mr. Slim Domit served as the Chief Executive Officer at Grupo Financiero Inbursa, S.A.B. de C.V. from August 25, 1997 to April 2012. Mr. Slim Domit ... provides the Board with knowledge and expertise in international finance and particular insight into emerging and Latin American markets. He has substantive expertise in developing new businesses in international markets, stockholder rights and business strategy and integration to the Board of Directors. He served as the Chief Executive Officer of Banco Inbursa, S.A. and Institución de Banca Múltiple. He serves as Chairman of Banco Inbursa, S.A., Institución de Banca Múltiple, Grupo Financiero Inbursa and has been its Director since April 26, 2002. He serves as Chairman of the Board of Directors of GCarso e IDEAL, Calos Slim de la Salud, A.C. and Fundación Inbursa, A.C. Mr. Slim Domit has been the Chairman of the Board of Directors of Grupo Financiero Inbursa SAB de CV August 25, 1997. He serves as the Chairman of The Carlos Slim Health Institute. He has been Non-Independent Chairman of Impulsora del Desarrollo y el Empleo en América Latina since April 2012 and serves as its Non-Independent Director. He served as Vice Chairman of Impulsora del Desarrollo y el Empleo en América Latina, S.A.B. de C.V. from April 2010 to April 2012. He also serves as Member of the Board of Directors of Fundación Carlos Slim, A.C. He serves as a Director of CGT and Telmex. He serves as a Director of Carso Global Telecom, S.A. de C.V., América Telecom S.A. de C.V., Inversora Bursátil, S.A. de C.V., Casa de Bolsa, Afore Inbursa, S.A. de C.V., Arrendadora Financiera Inbursa, S.A. de C.V., Fianzas Guardiana Inbursa, S.A., Operadora Inbursa de Sociedades de Inversión, S.A. de C.V., Seguros Inbursa, S.A. and of other subsidiaries of Grupo Financiero Inbursa and of some subsidiaries of Grupo Carso. He has been a Director of Sofom Inbursa, S.A. de C.V., SOFOM, ER, Grupo Financiero Inbursa since September 6, 2011. He serves as a Director of Grupo Carso, S.A.B. de C.V. He serves as a Director of Patrimonial Inbursa, S.A. Mr. Slim Domit has been an Independent Director of BlackRock, Inc. since September 26, 2011. Mr. Slim Domit served as a Member of the Board of Directors of Teléfonos de México, S.A.B. de C.V. from 1995 to April 2014. He served as a Director of Grupo Sanborns, S.A.B. de C.V. He holds a Bachelor's degree in Business Administration from the Universidad Anáhuac.Read Full Background




