Insider Activity


Individual




Marco Antonio Slim Domit



Mr. Marco Antonio Slim Domit is Independent Director at BlackRock, Inc., Chairman at Impulsora del Desarrollo y el Empleo en América Latina SAB, Chairman at Grupo Financiero Inbursa SAB de CV, Chairman at Instituto Carlos Slim de la Salud, Chairman at Seguros Inbursa SA, and Chairman at Inversora Bursatil SA de CV. He is on the Board of Directors at BlackRock, Inc., Grupo Carso SAB de CV, Carso Global Telecom SAB de CV, Banco Inbursa SA, and Inversora Carso SA de CV.
Mr. Slim Domit also served on the board at Teléfonos de México SAB de CV, America Movil SAB de CV, and Bolsa Mexicana de Valores SAB de CV.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Anahuac.



