Interests, Passion, Hobbies

Kind of Interests, Passion and Hobbies: Art
Description: Attended the 2011 inauguration of the Soumaya Museum, established by Slim Domit's father, Carlos Slim Helu. The museum displays Carlos Slim Helu's art collection, including Rodin's "Thinker," Rufino Tamayo's "Naturaleza Muerta" and other pieces by Vincent Van Gogh, Henri Matisse, Claude Monet and Salvador Dali.


Kind of Interests, Passion and Hobbies: Networking
Description: Attended the 2012 opening of the Bros Oyster Bar and Restaurant in Mexico DF, Mexico.


Kind of Interests, Passion and Hobbies: Health and Wellness
Description: Serves as President of the Instituto Carlos Slim de la Salud, a non-profit organization engaged in medical research.

